# CORTEX session (Prime Gate)

**Repo id**: `.repo-root.json` → `dame-luthas-app` (alias `dame-luthas`)  
**Default agent**: `181`  
**SSOT**: `../.agent-kb/db/agent_kb.sqlite` — not chat summaries or stale `.cortex-boot.json` alone.

Run all commands from **this repo root**. See `documentation-standards/docs/PRIME-GATE-AGENT-REVIEW.md`.

## Prime boot (every session start)

```bash
npx tsx ../.agent-kb/anvil/cortex-boot.mts --repo=dame-luthas-app --agent=181 --force
# or MCP: prime_boot
cat .cortex-boot.json
```

**Also read:** `.codebase-manifest.json`, `docs/PROJECT-OVERVIEW.md`, latest `docs/checkpoints/*.md`.

**Task query (when boot stale):**

```bash
sqlite3 ../.agent-kb/db/agent_kb.sqlite \
  "SELECT id, priority, status, substr(description,1,60) FROM tasks WHERE repo='dame-luthas-app' AND status!='complete' ORDER BY priority LIMIT 20;"
```

## During work

```bash
npx tsx ../.agent-kb/anvil/run.mts checkpoint --task={TASK_ID} --status=complete --repo=dame-luthas-app
```

Pre-commit: `npx tsc --noEmit && npm run lint && npm run build`

## Session end

```bash
npx tsx ../.agent-kb/anvil/run.mts close --session={SESSION_ID} --repo=dame-luthas-app
npx tsx ../.agent-kb/db/sync.mts --push
```

Claude macOS: `/exit` → `.claude/commands/exit.md`  
Cursor: `@exit` → `documentation-standards/skills/exit/SKILL.md`

**Production:** https://dameluthas.damieus.app
